"Grylli includes built-in instructions throughout the app to help you "
"configure and manage your setup."
msgstr ""
"Grylli iquka izikhokelo ezakhelwe ngaphakathi kwisicelo ukukunceda "
"uhlengahlengisa kwaye ulawule ulungiselelo lwakho."

#: app/templates/help.html:8
msgid ""
"This page provides an overview of key features and direct links to where "
"they can be managed."
msgstr ""
"Eli phepha libonelela ngesishwankathelo sezinto ezibalulekileyo kunye "
"neekhonkco ezicacileyo apho zinokulawulwa."

